<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-10">
      <div class="card shadow-lg border-0">
        <div class="card-body p-5">
          <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <div class="demo-badge my-3">
              <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark px-3 py-2">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-code me-2"></i>Demo Project Only
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="disclaimer alert alert-info mb-5">
            <h4 class="alert-heading">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info me-2"></i>Important Notice
            </h4>
            <p>
              <strong>WanderLust is a demo project</strong> created for
              educational and portfolio purposes by Anuraj Jit Saikia (aka
              Raja). This is not a real service. No actual user data is stored
              or used commercially. This project was built to showcase software
              development and design skills.
            </p>
          </div>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-database me-3" style="color: #fe424d"></i
              >Information We Collect
            </h2>
            <p>In a real application, we might collect information like:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                Personal identification information (name, email address, phone
                number, etc.)
              </li>
              <li>Account information (username, password)</li>
              <li>User-generated content (reviews, listings)</li>
              <li>
                Technical data (IP address, browser information, device
                information)
              </li>
              <li>Usage data (how you interact with our service)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              <strong>However, as this is a demo project</strong>, while the
              application may appear to collect this information, it is not used
              for commercial purposes and data persistence is limited to
              demonstration functionality only.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-gears me-3" style="color: #fe424d"></i>How
              We Use Your Information
            </h2>
            <p>
              In a commercial application, collected information might be used
              to:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Provide, maintain, and improve our services</li>
              <li>Process transactions and bookings</li>
              <li>Send transactional messages and service updates</li>
              <li>Respond to comments, questions, and requests</li>
              <li>
                Protect against, identify, and prevent fraud and other illegal
                activity
              </li>
              <li>
                Fulfill other purposes disclosed at the time of collection
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              <strong>As WanderLust is a demo project</strong>, any information
              entered is used solely to demonstrate the functionality of the
              application.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">
              <i
                class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved me-3"
                style="color: #fe424d"></i
              >Data Storage and Security
            </h2>
            <p>This demo application may use technologies such as:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                MongoDB (a NoSQL database) for storing listing and user
                information
              </li>
              <li>
                Cookies and local storage for maintaining sessions and user
                preferences
              </li>
              <li>Cloudinary for image storage and processing</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              <strong>Important:</strong> While we've implemented security
              measures appropriate for a demo project, WanderLust is not
              designed for production use or storing sensitive personal
              information.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-handshake me-3" style="color: #fe424d"></i
              >Third-Party Services
            </h2>
            <p>
              This demo application may integrate with third-party services
              including:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Mapbox for maps and geolocation services</li>
              <li>Authentication providers like Google and GitHub for OAuth</li>
              <li>Cloudinary for image storage</li>
              <li>MongoDB Atlas for database services</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              These integrations are implemented for demonstration purposes only
              and showcase integration capabilities.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="fw-bold">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope me-3" style="color: #fe424d"></i
              >Contact Information
            </h2>
            <p>
              This project was created by Anuraj Jit Saikia (Raja) as a
              portfolio project.
            </p>
            <p>For questions about this demo project, you can reach out via:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                GitHub:
                <a href="https://github.com/Anuraj-dev" target="_blank"
                  >github.com/Anuraj-dev</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>Demo purposes only</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <div class="text-center mt-5">
            <a href="<%= referer %>" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left me-2"></i>Go Back
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .demo-badge {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  section {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  section h2 {
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
</style>
